{"tid":1699524,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[推上熱門] 今晚不宜開花！！！！！！！","createTime":"2019-11-08T05:09:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-08T07:26:42.000Z","uid":22885,"like":88,"dislike":359,"uniUserReply":132,"replies":[{"pid":"ec4c691b94788fdfe44c9a127879d782211cbede","tid":1699524,"uid":22885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T05:09:56.000Z","msg":"周同學係死咗 係要攞返公道 係要黑警填命 <br />\n<br />\n但係點攞公道？ 單純話今晚開花 星期六日開花 <br />\n又再預告比啲曱甴知我地開花 你嚟圍捕啦 咁樣？<br />\n<br />\n我地攞公道 抗爭 革命唔應該係咁樣<br />\n<br />\n而家嘅我地 衰啲講句 毫無對策 <br />\n<br />\n而家嘅大型集會 有冇不反都好 曱甴都照當你非法集會 又係拉幾十個幾百個手足返去 傷嘅傷 死嘅死 <br />\n<br />\n我地係要一直都咁做咩？咁樣攞咩公道 公道唔係用更多嘅手足嚟換架<br />\n<br />\n我知有好多人好嬲好傷心好想做啲野 <br />\n<br />\n但係貿貿然開花 集會 <br />\n比機會佢地拉多好多人 殺好多手足<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係一啲都唔值得同冇用！！！！</span>"},{"pid":"29b0b6e1decc4e2260e0380dac2001cee0a60d2a","tid":1699524,"uid":263618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T05:10:32.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e3590a223d3ae2c215146b6e939121f60e364b1a","tid":1699524,"uid":1634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T05:12:21.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2887bb91fd51ec8f256466d720bea7557d9259ff","tid":1699524,"uid":67813,"like":39,"dislike":10,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T05:12:43.000Z","msg":"又黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又要計劃一個月？"},{"pid":"d9c4fa36a5ae1cec8bf673042ae69adf12c1f9dc","tid":1699524,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T05:13:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bf85c6fd4ad082d9454a5e2e87c2a628d422862","tid":1699524,"uid":254114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T05:13:32.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid":"027bbe1f2054ab7207979a49567ad098acc3b11c","tid":1699524,"uid":182061,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T05:13:33.000Z","msg":"開花係不如突發"},{"pid":"c25bf7d21593ba8