人習性大家都知 拖長泥講 無目的好多人都未必出泥<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記唔記得7月1 8月5 大講講到最後一戰咁有個目標 自然會多人出泥<br />\n<br />\n民意冇減少 但係成日咩宣傳都冇突然間就情緒發洩叫人出嚟 係條街上又唔係個個人心理準備對抗 <br />\nPopo一泥 就要跪低被捕 <br />\n<br />\n唔該大家影清楚啲事實 <br />\n未準備好ga 和理非都唔好沖去商場 到時唔開鋪 全港都冇得消費 要去幫襯街鋪黃店<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a8ae720af1e3b8a50910c790a64c249a5630fa7","tid":1699524,"uid":129068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T05:27:34.000Z","msg":"善用不推文回覆"},{"pid":"2501ded78eea6bcb212a2a5eac0ae3b46f8748ce","tid":1699524,"uid":41507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T05:27:42.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"3e1f811ed7d7a7e7d09550aa4c48e8a278c4d354","tid":1699524,"uid":226569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T05:28:23.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"e56b8ce8742963a3566732d4768e7f26908ec0a2","tid":1699524,"uid":5320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T05:28:23.000Z","msg":"等人權法 休息下 要和理非"},{"pid":"f2ab3f2cff3e8e986577f32f759aed699ccefd90","tid":1699524,"uid":1988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T05:28:28.000Z","msg":"洗唔洗同黑警申請不反對通知書先呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc275af378af15f4bef92ce1b501029bc7978de4","tid":1699524,"uid":60033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T05:28:33.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"65782dc7c65057eaa616d3181f45ceb5e4445e13","tid":1699524,"uid":258566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T05:28:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ab701e88cf39b1ad09f62b6b67d2a0842227d140","tid":1699524,"uid":255106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T05:28:51.000Z","msg":"手捉小心D"},{"pid":"059d8b609b400e35552b85a65e56613b33b5521c","tid":16